high_descs: Turn left and walk to the sink on the right.
Pick up the bar of soap to the right in the sink.
Turn around and walk to the black bin to the right of the toilet.
Put the soap inside of the black bin.
Turn around and walk back over to the sink.
Pick up the bar of soap from the sink.
Turn around and walk back to the black bin.
Put the bar of soap inside the black bin and to the right of the first bar of soap.
anns.task_desc: To move two bars of soap to the black bin.

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the wall, then hang a right and walk up to the sink.
Pick up the rightmost bar of soap out of the sink basin.
Turn left and walk over to the wall, then hang a left and walk up to the small black bin on the ground.
Put the bar of soap in the small black bin.
Walk back over to the sink behind you.
Pick up the bar of soap out of the sink.
Turn left and walk over to the wall, then turn left and walk up to the small black bin in the corner of the room.
Put the bar of soap into the small black bin.
anns.task_desc: Move two bars of soap from the sink to a small black bin.
